>Step 3: Test the Checkbox</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>The final step is to test the checkbox to ensure that it is working correctly. To test the checkbox, follow these steps:</p>\n\n\n\n<p>1. Go to your store&#8217;s checkout page.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>2. Add a product to your cart and proceed to the checkout page.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>3. Check the box next to the terms and conditions checkbox.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>4. Click the Place Order button to complete your purchase.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>5. If the purchase is successful, then the checkbox is working correctly, and customers must agree to the terms and conditions before making a purchase.</p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center\"><br><br><div data-gatsby-image-wrapper=\"\" style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;display:inline-block;vertical-align:top\" class=\"gatsby-image-wrapper gatsby-image-wrapper-constrained  inline-gatsby-image-wrapper\"><div style=\"max-width:645px;display:block\"><img alt=\"\" role=\"presentation\" aria-hidden=\"true\" src=\"data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg%20height=&#x27;385&#x27;%20width=&#x27;645&#x27;%20xmlns=&#x27;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%20version=&#x27;1.1&#x27;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" style=\"max-width:100%;display:block;position:static\"/></div><div aria-hidden=\"true\" data-placeholder-image=\"\" style=\"height:100%;left:0;position:absolute;top:0;width:100%\"></div><img data-gatsby-image-ssr=\"\" data-wp-inline-image=\"3\" data-main-image=\"\" style=\"height:100%;left:0;position:absolute;top:0;transform:translateZ(0);transition:opacity 250ms linear;width:100%;will-change:opacity;opacity:0\" sizes=\"(min-width: 645px) 645px, 100vw\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" data-src=\"/_gatsby/image/113934290708308d7644260b77481c2a/15daa056ca836efbb0ecd37dc07bedba/cefcc84bd656248ac5439a33245d60dd.png?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebguru.dev%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2Fcefcc84bd656248ac5439a33245d60dd.png&amp;a=w%3D161%26h%3D96%26fm%3Dpng%26q%3D90&amp;cd=2023-06-15T10%3A20%3A38\" data-srcset=\"/_gatsby/image/113934